  "title": "Masseur, Massage Therapist (Including Foot Reflexology)",
  "description": "<p>Job Descriptions</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide consistent professional spa massage (body and/or foot) in accordance with spa standards.</li>\n  <li>Ensure high level of service standards</li>\n  <li>Responsible for the maintenance of cleanliness and neaness of the spa facilities, treatment rooms and other parts of the spa.</li>\n  <li>Responsible in preparing the necessary treatment products, replenishment of stocks, towels supply etc.</li>\n  <li>Handle customer queries and conerns effcieintly and politely</li>\n  <li>Follow and comply with the intrucstions given by Spa Manager</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Preperably with iTEC/WSQ certification or massage certification</li>\n  <li>Able to commit on Weekends/public holidays</li>\n  <li>6 days work week</li>\n  <li>Mininum one year relevant experience</li>\n  <li>Pleasant personality and hardworking</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Benefits</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Attractive Salary</li>\n  <li>Conducive working environment</li>\n</ul>",
